; Forecast results should be ordered by date when mixing periodic
; transactions with different intervals (e.g. monthly and yearly).
~ Monthly
    Expense:MonthlyExpense           $11.00
    Assets

~ Yearly
    Expenses:YearlyExpense   $88.00
    Assets

test reg --forecast 'date<[2016/04]' --now=2015/11/15 --columns 80
15-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Expenses:YearlyExpense       $88.00       $88.00
15-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-88.00            0
15-Nov-01 Forecast transaction  Expense:MonthlyExpense       $11.00       $11.00
15-Nov-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-11.00            0
15-Dec-01 Forecast transaction  Expense:MonthlyExpense       $11.00       $11.00
15-Dec-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-11.00            0
16-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Expense:MonthlyExpense       $11.00       $11.00
16-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-11.00            0
16-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Expenses:YearlyExpense       $88.00       $88.00
16-Jan-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-88.00            0
16-Feb-01 Forecast transaction  Expense:MonthlyExpense       $11.00       $11.00
16-Feb-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-11.00            0
16-Mar-01 Forecast transaction  Expense:MonthlyExpense       $11.00       $11.00
16-Mar-01 Forecast transaction  Assets                      $-11.00            0
end test
